Type: Package
Package: rprimer
Title: Design RT-PCR Assays from Multiple Sequence Alignments
Version: 0.99.0
Description: rprimer provides functions to design
    primers, probes and PCR assays from multiple sequence alignments of
    DNA sequences, based on user specified constraints. 
    For more information about the package and its 
    functionality, please see thee vingette.
